description: The body of a 39-year-old woman was found in Ramsey on Sunday morning, Isle of Man Constabulary say.
title: Isle of Man police investigate after woman's body found in woodland
title_page: Isle of Man police investigate after woman's body found in woodland - BBC News
maintext: A police investigation has been launched into the death of a woman whose body was found in a woodland in the north of the Isle of Man.
